00:35:42.120 --> 00:35:43.140
campaign.

00:35:43.140 --> 00:35:45.990
And for five years, that was
the only funding we had--

00:35:45.990 --> 00:35:46.950
so $11,000.

00:35:46.950 --> 00:35:50.955
Civilization, this incredible
design firm in Seattle

00:35:50.955 --> 00:35:52.890
who just won the
Cooper Hewitt Award

00:35:52.890 --> 00:35:57.340
