you want to do a dinner,

00:36:40.830 --> 00:36:43.290
just like a board
game, here it is.

00:36:43.290 --> 00:36:44.340
It's on you.

00:36:44.340 --> 00:36:45.330
Make it happen.

00:36:45.330 --> 00:36:47.280
So that was our model,
really, just because

00:36:47.280 --> 00:36:48.120
of the lack of resources.

00:36:48.120 --> 00:36:48.490
DAVID LEVIN: Yeah.

00:36:48.490 --> 00:36:50.010
So you talk about
lack of resources.

00:36:50.010 --> 00:36:51.600
In other cases, I
think I've heard

00:36:51.600 --> 00:36:55.440
you refer to the website and
its presentation as a gift.

00:36:55.440 --> 00:36:57.880
Why is that important to
you that it's like a gift?

00:36:57.880 --> 00:36:58.050
MICHAEL HEBB: Yeah.

