But he is involved
in that as well.

00:38:23.838 --> 00:38:27.085
I was thinking of the commons--

00:38:27.085 --> 00:38:28.210
AUDIENCE: Creative Commons.

00:38:28.210 --> 00:38:31.170
MICHAEL HEBB: Creative Commons,
yeah, inspired in great part

